@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.74 + (tmp + 0.21 - tmp + 0.78)) - ((tmp + 0.89 - v0 + 0.08) - (v0 + 0.09 + v2 + 0.16)))
    tmp = wp.abs(v0)
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.21) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.38)) * tmp)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.13)) + wp.sin(wp.abs(v2 + 0.13)))
    v0 = ((v0 * (tmp + 0.70 * tmp + 0.79)) + wp.sin((tmp + 0.17 + tmp + 0.29)))
    v2 = ((v2 * v1) * v0)
    v1 = wp.cos(v0)
    v0 = (v1 * ((tmp + 0.83 - v0 + 0.13) * tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
